---
// Final Hero Component (v5)
// - No Badge
// - Uppercase Bruta Headers
// - Centered Layout
---

<section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 overflow-hidden bg-[#FFF8E9] text-black">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      
      {/* 1. Main Heading */}
      <div class="relative mb-8 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
         <h1 class="font-bruta text-6xl md:text-8xl leading-[0.9] uppercase relative z-0 text-[#FF5507]">
            {/* Note: I added text-[#FF5507] (Orange) just in case, but usually it's black in your design? 
                index.html shows standard text color. If it should be black, remove text-[#FF5507] */}
            <span class="block text-black">YOUR LOADING DOCK,</span>
            <span class="block text-black">YOUR RULES</span>
         </h1>
      </div>

      {/* 2. Subheading */}
      <p class="font-recoleta text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Our dock scheduling software is known for having the easiest interface and the most helpful team in the industry.
        <br />
        <strong class="text-black block mt-4">Start turning trucks around faster today.</strong>
      </p>

      {/* 3. Form Area */}
      <div class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto mb-16">
        <form 
          action="https://calendly.com/nick-rakovsky/datadocks-demo" 
          target="_blank"
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3"
        >
          <input 
            type="email" 
            placeholder="Enter your email" 
            class="flex-1 h-12 px-4 rounded-lg border border-[#EFE2D2] bg-white text-black focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#FF5507]"
            required
          />
          <button 
            type="submit"
            class="h-12 px-8 bg-[#FF5507] hover:bg-[#ff6a2b] text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl whitespace-nowrap uppercase tracking-wide text-sm"
          >
            Schedule a Demo
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

      {/* 4. Hero Image */}
      <div class="relative w-full rounded-xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden border border-[#EFE2D2] bg-white">
        <img 
          src="/images/DataDocks-Calendar-Screenshot.webp" 
          alt="DataDocks Calendar Interface" 
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>